---
import ServicePageLayout from '../../layouts/ServicePageLayout.astro';
---

<ServicePageLayout
  title="Indoor Air Quality | HiLo Heating & Air"
  description="Breathe easier with our air purifiers, filtration systems, and duct cleaning services. Expert indoor air quality solutions in Orange County."
  heroTitle="Indoor Air Quality"
  heroSubtitle="Breathe easier with our air purifiers, filtration systems, and duct cleaning services."
>
  <section class="pt-4 sm:pt-8 pb-16 sm:pb-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-lg">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-blue mt-0 mb-4">Improving Your Home’s Indoor Air Quality</h2>

      <p>Indoor air quality is essential for your health and comfort. HiLo Heating & Air Conditioning installs air purifiers, humidifiers, filtration systems, and complete ductwork to improve indoor air quality and create healthier, more comfortable home environments year-round.</p>

      <h2>Why Indoor Air Quality Matters</h2>
      <p>The air inside your home can be two to five times more polluted than outdoor air. Dust, allergens, mold spores, pet dander, and chemical pollutants circulate through your HVAC system every day. For families with allergies, asthma, or respiratory sensitivities, this can make a significant difference in daily comfort and long-term health.</p>

      <h2>Our Indoor Air Quality Solutions</h2>
      <p>We offer a complete range of indoor air quality services tailored to your home's specific needs:</p>

      <h3>Air Purifiers</h3>
      <p>Advanced air purification systems that remove allergens, bacteria, and pollutants from your home's air. We install whole-home purifiers that work with your existing HVAC system to filter every room.</p>

      <h3>Humidifiers</h3>
      <p>Maintain optimal humidity levels for comfort and health. Dry air can cause respiratory irritation, static electricity, and damage to wood furniture. We install and maintain whole-home humidifiers that integrate with your heating system.</p>

      <h3>Filtration Systems</h3>
      <p>High-efficiency filtration systems that trap dust, pollen, pet dander, and other airborne particles. We help you choose the right MERV rating for your system and lifestyle.</p>

      <h3>Duct Cleaning</h3>
      <p>Professional duct cleaning to remove accumulated dust, debris, and contaminants from your ductwork. Clean ducts improve air quality, system efficiency, and reduce allergens throughout your home.</p>

      <h2>How We Approach Indoor Air Quality</h2>
      <p>Every home is different. We start by assessing your current air quality, identifying problem areas, and recommending solutions that fit your budget and needs. Whether you need a simple filter upgrade or a complete air purification system, we'll walk you through your options and let you decide.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-8 text-center">Related Services</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {[
          { title: 'Duct Installation', desc: 'New ductwork for better airflow and air quality.', href: '/duct-installation/' },
          { title: 'Duct Sealing', desc: 'Seal leaky ducts to improve efficiency and air quality.', href: '/hvac-duct-sealing/' },
          { title: 'HVAC Humidifier', desc: 'Whole-home humidity control for healthier air.', href: '/hvac-humidifier/' },
        ].map((svc) => (
          <a href={svc.href} class="bg-white border border-brand-blue/10 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-brand-blue/30 transition-all group">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2 group-hover:text-brand-red transition-colors">{svc.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-4">{svc.desc}</p>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue group-hover:text-brand-red transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-1">
              Learn More
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" /></svg>
            </span>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServicePageLayout>
